query:
UPDATE tukin_policies
        SET
          effective_from = $2,
          effective_to = $3,
          missing_checkout_penalty_pct = $4::DOUBLE PRECISION,
          late_tolerance_minutes = $5,
          late_penalty_per_minute_pct = $6,
          max_daily_penalty_pct = $7,
          out_of_geofence_penalty_pct = $8,
          updated_at = now()
        WHERE id = $1
        RETURNING id
